author: claudep
message:
Fixed #18684 -- Added Finnish DATETIME_FORMAT

Thanks Guttorm Flatab√∏ for the report and the initial patch.

files.patch:
@@ -7,7 +7,7 @@

+DATETIME_FORMAT = r'j. E Y \k\e\l\l\o G.i.s'

 MONTH_DAY_FORMAT = 'j. F'
 SHORT_DATE_FORMAT = 'j.n.Y'
